Build an ASP.NET Razor Pages application in C# that recreates the functionality shown in the screenshots in the Legacy-Screenshots folder.

The main Index page should have buttons or links for all the standard database operations like adding records, viewing data, and filtering results.

Aim for a clean, modern user interface similar to this example:
https://cdn.dribbble.com/userupload/4279134/file/original-5e630140a5ad559268aaf9fd3650b403.png?resize=2048x1536&vertical=center

Target .NET 8 (the current Long Term Support version):

    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>


